cff-version: 1.2.0
message: >
  If you use the AuraWear software, please cite this software release using
  the metadata below. For the associated C&C 2026 research publication,
  please see the publication citation in README.md.
type: software
title: "AuraWear Analysis"
abstract: >
  AuraWear is a human-in-the-loop fashion recommendation system integrating
  personal color analysis with LLM-driven intent understanding. The system
  diagnoses the user's 12-season personal color type from a selfie, constructs
  a curated seasonal palette, and recommends clothing items through a
  multi-signal reranking pipeline with real-time preference learning.
authors:
